  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Conceptualizing Language Learning App**\n\nI\'m now focusing on a language learning app that generates short stories tailored to CEFR levels. I\'m aiming for roughly 500 words per chapter. The plan is for stories to be 7 chapters long. The focus has moved from broader app functionality to this core storytelling engine.\n\n\n**Expanding Story Length and Features**\n\nI\'ve decided to extend the stories to 10 chapters. A vocabulary builder will now accompany each chapter. I\'ll include Google Docs export for easy reading and implement a polished and switchable dark mode UI. Regarding skills, Gemini API, Workspace integration, and OAuth integration are all required.\n\n\n"
