enting Google Docs Integration**\n\nI\'m now figuring out the Google Docs integration. The goal is client-side implementation. I\'m focusing on structuring the project. I\'ve decided to create a dedicated file, `/src/lib/auth.ts`, for Firebase Auth and Google API helper functions. I\'ve also identified a crucial dependency: `firebase-applet-config.json` for Firebase configuration, and discovered it\'s missing in the initial project structure, and now trying to recall how Auth works in the AI studio.\n\n\n"
