r-side. Additionally, I\'m now curious about whether the frontend in AI Studio Build has access to `window.google`. I\'ll explore this as a potential authentication strategy.\n\n\n**Examining Firebase Configuration**\n\nI\'m now investigating the Firebase configuration further. I\'m wondering whether the backend handles the OAuth callback, or if it is the frontend. I\'m checking the standard workspace integration skill again and, noting that the Firebase project is already provisioned, I\'m now looking for `firebase-applet-config.json`. Despite the failure, I\'m wondering if it already exists, possibly hidden. I\'m going to search recursively, then check the `set_up_firebase` parameters, focusing on potential empty values for `FirebaseProjectID` or `firestoreRegion`.\n\n\n"
